##Who would have thought, this Spring Festival should be the stock of the year mask | Sandwich

WECHAT china30s

Feature description, a platform that encourages you to write about your life. Founded in March 2011, it has a sandwich writing school and a media platform, China Sandwich, at the same time, we are committed to applying the story to cross-border product design, urban culture excavation, exhibition fair, space creation and other three-dimensional field.

By H≈çno
Coordinates: Sichuan
Occupation: Media Man

1

In the morning, I use diluted 84 disinfectant, wearing a two-day disposable medical mask spray inside and outside, air in the ventilation, the afternoon to go to work can also cope with the use. By the way, the toilet, floor drain, coat, door handle also spray again, even go out to wear the soles of the shoes are not let go.

Who would have thought, this Spring Festival should be the most reserve year goods, is the mask. Until Academician Zhong Nanshan came out and said, to prevent new coronavirus infection, must wear a mask, because confirmed the risk of human-to-human transmission.

I did not join the rush because I happened to have a small stock of masks in my home, and because I did not foresee that the outbreak would be a protracted battle of popular participation, assuming the family masks would be able to handle it.

Who has a spare mask at home? Thanks to my husband. Two months ago, he suffered a sudden facial spasm, commonly known as facial paralysis, in the hospital pharmacy bought two packets of disposable protective masks, a total of 20, during his treatment to shield him from the wind and ugliness. Because his face plate is large, mask appears small, cover not tight, I also bought a wide-width thick cotton mask in winter on the Internet, put his big cake face wrapped up. Buy more have preferential benefit, then bought 3, trichromatic at one go, the population of a family. They come in handy when the epidemic is on the rise and masks are not available online or offline.

I remember the first time I wore a mask seriously, it was in 2003 during SARS. At that time when reporters, to interview the special treatment of Medical Waste Waste, my colleagues gave me a gauze mask, put on to go. That year really did not fear, this year's new coronavirus pneumonia epidemic, the high rate of infection, the spread of a wide range of infectious ways, really frightening. If someone is not wearing a mask, you think he (She) is intentional.

These days, as well as reminding people to wear masks, experts and the media teach them the correct way to wear masks and wash their hands as patiently and repeatedly as they teach kindergartners. There are also plenty of ways to urge people to wear masks. Today, I saw a place on my cell phone that was monitored by a drone, and if I saw anyone not wearing one, I hovered over their heads and shouted at you.

Actually, I hate wearing a mask. It makes it hard to breathe. When climbing Snow Mountain with a magic turban to cover the mouth and nose windbreak, will also have a high anti-aggravating breathless feeling. But in the winter of 2016, I had to put on a mask to protect myself from PM2.5. To relieve the discomfort in my mouth and nose, and to protect my lungs.

That year, Sichuan Basin's smog was thick and persistent, with visibility of less than five meters on the roads, and the city's iconic red tilt-a-la-la-la bridge looming like a mirage amid the gray haze. "I plunged into the night as I plunged into the pool, as if feeling the sticky, foul air breaking through and closing behind me, " Booven wrote

In the winter of 2017, I bought 123M N95 anti-haze masks at one go, just in case of winter. Results that winter, thanks to environmental protection, the smog is not as serious as the first year, mask only used two, and I generously gave a few to others. In the two years that followed, the smog still came in the winter, less ominous than in 2016. I already consider the rest of the masks to be covers.

When the new coronavirus epidemic hit, they all said that N95 was the king of anti-foam masks, and I immediately thought of them. Rummaging through the drawers, only finding one in the bathroom drawer.

Now it lay on several tables, like a white bat.

I was embarrassed to go out, because the N95 masks of the first-line medical staff are not enough, we ordinary people have disposable medical mask protection, is good enough.

2

It's my 10th day in a row. Three days ago, the unit just issued to the first-line staff two disposable medical masks. Xiao Wang waited in line for two hours before running to the city government's distribution window on a cold night to get the first batch of 150 masks.

Today, the unit is expected to give each person two, the result of the office said that we have not been able to uniform from the market to the mask, is anxious to fire to think of ways to do it.

Dozens of reporters outside the epidemic prevention and control, hospitals, communities, shopping malls, cities and villages, drilling everywhere, there is no useful mask, great risk. Editors spend eight or nine hours a day in a large office and sit together in pre editing meetings; the editorial and publishing departments work together in front of a computer, designing the layout, and taking large samples for redaction. It's impossible to keep a distance of two meters at all times. Not Without a mask.

Every night shift the last off-duty publishing department ade, the face of a disposable mask, was a chubby face strained almost transparent. "I've been wearing it for five or six days, " he said, and I unconsciously took a few steps away from him. Tell him that his disposable face mask, protective coating has been worn away, where still can withstand the attack of droplets. It is better to learn to poke four holes in the mouth with a grapefruit peel wear some rope to use, at least thick, also tangy grapefruit. The paradox is that we ourselves suffer from a lack of masks, but the directive above can not mention this in the script, so as not to cause bad public opinion.

For example, this news, there are a pair of lovely brother and sister, want to use the lucky money to buy a mask for the police uncle, but can not buy, had to donate 200 yuan, but also hand-written a letter of respect, it mentioned that can not buy a mask this matter, child talk without restraint. The video news shows the letter in childish handwriting. Was asked to withdraw, "can not buy a mask" after the word rid of the re-sent.

In other news, villagers in one village stepped on sewing machines and made their own masks out of cotton cloth. Well, this is awkward. This is the grass-roots epidemic prevention and control of folk wisdom and innovative action, is the top requirements for reporters to dig up the typical highlights, but also reflects an indisputable fact: we have to use cloth sewing mask, clearly, is unable to buy, Lack Bai.

Today, someone on the mobile phone spread the news of a department, said that the public can go to the number of pharmacies in the city, with ID cards a person limit to buy three masks, announced a long list of pharmacies and address. I hurried out the door with the ID cards of a family of three to verify the good news.

As a result, ran a few streets, there is no such thing, the door wrote a few big words, "no masks to sell. ". Ask If there's any tomorrow, and say no. Looks like we got the wrong information.

Think these days mask manufacturers back to work rate rise, mask is not as recently in short supply, who knows several groups are talking about masks.

Shanghai students to introduce the Shanghai method, you can make an appointment with the community, the community statistics, go to the Department of material distribution after collection. First-line big city's safeguard, causes other schoolmates to envy. Neighbor Ms. Zhang is a property management company manager, responsible for the management of the building's public areas, including the daily cleaning and disinfection of the elevator, more than 100 employees under the early resumption of work, mask demand. Many employees have been wearing disposable masks for days, she said.

She ordered 2000 disposable medical masks through a friend in the mask factory, worried about delivery insurance, and wait for urgent use, they drove to Chengdu to pick up, only to friends told her only 500, the other was transferred by a state-owned enterprise requisitioned; In fact, all of the transfer, these 500 are friends from their own order out of spare money back to her. She was stupid on the spot. She didn't think there was a robbery.

In response to Ms. Zhang's experience, someone in the group brought out China's emergency response law, saying that it is now a first-class response, uh, the Government May, when necessary, requisition from units and individuals equipment, facilities, sites, means of transportation and other materials needed for emergency rescue. Ms. Zhang is very aggrieved, "the government commandeers also just, why does a state-owned enterprise call my mask? "

Xiao Zhang got the duck to fly, but compared to the following several half-way cut off Hu things, it is not a matter of fact.

First there was the "Dali" unreasonable, Chongqing hard-won from overseas collection of N94 masks, protective clothing, disinfectant and other anti-epidemic equipment seized at the customs, lost each other a "temporary requisition notice. The severity of the outbreak is second only to that of Chongqing in Hubei Province, which is counting on the supplies, including supplies raised for Huangshi in Hubei Province, to be brought to the forefront of the fight against the disease. It was later revealed that the rescue equipment and materials purchased by Qingdao from Japan were seized and requisitioned by the Shenyang Customs. However, the Qingdao Customs found that a batch of masks that Shenyang had collected from South Korea would enter the customs from Qingdao. Therefore, the Qingdao side urged the customs to intercept them, reciprocal requisition. Netizens called it a war "epidemic" in the direct line and the Fengxi dispute.

The initial underestimation of the enemy led to a local war "epidemic" evolved into a civil war, 1.4 billion people have to face masks, how can there be no shortage of masks?

Editors spend eight or nine hours a day in a large office and sit together in pre editing meetings; the editorial and publishing departments work together in front of a computer, designing the layout, and taking large samples for redaction. "I've been wearing it for five or six days, " he said, and I unconsciously took a few steps away from him. In other news, villagers in one village stepped on sewing machines and made their own masks out of cotton cloth. Well, this is awkward. This is the grass-roots epidemic prevention and control of folk wisdom and innovative action, is the top requirements for reporters to dig up the typical highlights, but also reflects an indisputable fact: we have to use cloth sewing mask, clearly, is unable to buy, Lack Bai.

Think these days mask manufacturers back to work rate rise, mask is not as recently in short supply, who knows several groups are talking about masks.

Shanghai students to introduce the Shanghai method, you can make an appointment with the community, the community statistics, go to the Department of material distribution after collection. First-line big city's safeguard, causes other schoolmates to envy. Neighbor Ms. Zhang is a property management company manager, responsible for the management of the building's public areas, including the daily cleaning and disinfection of the elevator, more than 100 employees under the early resumption of work, mask demand. Many employees have been wearing disposable masks for days, she said.

She ordered 2000 disposable medical masks through a friend in the mask factory, worried about delivery insurance, and wait for urgent use, they drove to Chengdu to pick up, only to friends told her only 500, the other was transferred by a state-owned enterprise requisitioned; In fact, all of the transfer, these 500 are friends from their own order out of spare money back to her. She was stupid on the spot. She didn't think there was a robbery.

In response to Ms. Zhang's experience, someone in the group brought out China's emergency response law, saying that it is now a first-class response, uh, the Government May, when necessary, requisition from units and individuals equipment, facilities, sites, means of transportation and other materials needed for emergency rescue. Ms. Zhang is very aggrieved, "the government commandeers also just, why does a state-owned enterprise call my mask? "

The severity of the outbreak is second only to that of Chongqing in Hubei Province, which is counting on the supplies, including supplies raised for Huangshi in Hubei Province, to be brought to the forefront of the fight against the disease. It was later revealed that the rescue equipment and materials purchased by Qingdao from Japan were seized and requisitioned by the Shenyang Customs. However, the Qingdao Customs found that a batch of masks that Shenyang had collected from South Korea would enter the customs from Qingdao. Therefore, the Qingdao side urged the customs to intercept them, reciprocal requisition. Netizens called it a war "epidemic" in the direct line and the Fengxi dispute.
